title: No development of any sort shall be allowed in this zone except the project of the Forest Department
clause_text: No development of any sort shall be allowed in this zone except the project of the Forest Department. In case of pockets of private lands in G - 3 zone, development shall be permitted as per the provisions of Green Zone / as per the provisions of G - 1 / G - 2 Zone subject to concurrence of Forest Department.
section: Regulations for G - 3 Zone for Forest Area
